(enablePrefetching, numRCQEntries).explanation: Enabling prefetching increases memory requests which requires more request completion queue entries to handle the additional outstanding requests;

(enablePrefetching, power).explanation: Enabling prefetching increases processor activity through additional memory accesses and cache operations, directly leading to higher overall power consumption;

(enablePrefetching, power_pad).explanation: Prefetching increases I/O activity and signal transitions at processor pads, leading to higher pad power consumption;
